159
00:15:08,180 --> 00:15:13,900
And it can serve to transfer breathing machines or sputum aspirators.

160
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:20,340
Now we need to collect cases, so we need a lot of help from patients.

161
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:22,660
- I do have a suggestion. 
 - Go ahead.

162
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:25,940
I studied Internet Big Data Analysis in college.

163
00:15:25,940 --> 00:15:30,520
The most effective way is to build a big data platform,

164
00:15:30,520 --> 00:15:34,440
