165
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:38,180
Then we'd ask the patients to fill in all their questions on the scale.

166
00:15:38,180 --> 00:15:41,860
So that we can get the information that is timely and accurate.

167
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:45,760
This is really convenient, saving us time to ask them one by one.

168
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,320
That doesn't build scale.

169
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:51,280
