170
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:52,680
I can do it.

171
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:56,660
You can't do this alone. It takes a team.

172
00:15:56,660 --> 00:16:01,440
But a team requires funding. Funding is the biggest problem now.

173
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:04,960
