178
00:16:24,180 --> 00:16:25,040
Okay.

179
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:27,780
I don't have time on this project.

180
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:30,780
You work out a solution and then report back to me.

181
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:35,620
