213
00:19:06,040 --> 00:19:08,820
Right. Human makes miracles.

214
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:12,700
A hundred years ago, we couldn't have imagined such high technology today. I have confidence.

215
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:16,260
