216
00:19:16,260 --> 00:19:21,260
With your educational level, you have confidence in your career, but your career doesn't.

217
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:22,780
Chen Guangpu, what do you mean?

218
00:19:22,780 --> 00:19:27,460
